item.title: CVE-2017-2104|2024-08-05T13:39:32.317Z -- k-opticom%20corporation -- business%20lala%20call%20app%20for%20android
item.description: The Business LaLa Call App for Android 1.4.7 and earlier does not verify X.509 certificates from SSL servers, which allows man-in-the-middle attackers to spoof servers and obtain sensitive information via a crafted certificate.
